{"0":null,"0-2":{"rawHtml":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"utf-8\" />\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width,initial-scale=1\" />\n    <title>About Me</title>\n    <meta name=\"description\" content=\"About Connor, a networking and security practitioner who also works in data analytics, and the creator of the Tangent technical blog.\">\n    <link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https://codingatmyjob.github.io/sidebar/About.html\">\n\n    <meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"profile\">\n    <meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"About Connor | Tangent\">\n    <meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Networking and security practitioner, data science practitioner, and creator of Tangent.\">\n    <meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https://codingatmyjob.github.io/sidebar/About.html\">\n    <meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"https://codingatmyjob.github.io/images/cover/og-image.png\">\n    <meta property=\"og:image:alt\" content=\"Tangent technical blog preview image\">\n\n    <meta name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"summary_large_image\">\n    <meta name=\"twitter:title\" content=\"About Connor | Tangent\">\n    <meta name=\"twitter:description\" content=\"Networking and security practitioner, data science practitioner, and creator of Tangent.\">\n    <meta name=\"twitter:image\" content=\"https://codingatmyjob.github.io/images/cover/og-image.png\">\n\n    <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n    {\n        \"@context\": \"https://schema.org\",\n        \"@type\": \"Person\",\n        \"name\": \"Connor\",\n        \"url\": \"https://codingatmyjob.github.io/sidebar/About.html\",\n        \"jobTitle\": \"Networking & Security Practitioner | Data Science\",\n        \"sameAs\": [\n            \"https://github.com/codingatmyjob\",\n            \"https://www.credly.com/users/connor-rasmussen.58b75ec0/badges#credly\",\n            \"https://app.hackthebox.com/profile/2578864\"\n        ]\n    }\n    </script>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"../style.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div id=\"binary-bg\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div>\n\n    <main class=\"article-container\">\n        <h1>About Me</h1>\n\n        <article>\n            <div style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 40px;\">\n                <img src=\"/images/cover/profile.jpg\" style=\"width: 150px; height: 150px; border-radius: 50%; border: 3px solid var(--accent); margin-bottom: 20px;\">\n                <h2 style=\"font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 10px; color: var(--text-primary);\">Connor</h2>\n                <div style=\"font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--text-primary); opacity: 0.8;\">Networking & Security Practitioner | Data Science</div>\n            </div>\n\n            <h2>Who I Am</h2>\n            <p>Hi I'm Connor, and welcome to my technical blog, Tangent. Tangent is a space where I'm able to build a practical \n                project portfolio by sharing questions I've asked myself and answers I've uncovered. Here you'll find technical notes, project builds, experiments, reviews, and practical writeups.\n                While networking and cybersecurity were originally intended as the primary focus of this blog, I also do a lot of data science work that I will continue to develop in parallel.</p>\n            \n            <h2>Education & Experience</h2>\n            <ul>\n                <li>AAS in Network Systems Management</li>\n                <li>4 years of hands-on experience with Cisco networking equipment</li>\n                <li>5 years experience developing webapps, data analytics, and UI flows</li>\n\n            </ul>\n            \n            <h2>Technical Skills</h2>\n            <ul>\n                <li>Front-end Web Development → Building responsive and user-friendly interfaces</li>\n                <li>Jupyter Notebooks → Creating 'big data' analytics and automated solutions</li>\n                <li>Cisco → Configuration, troubleshooting, and deployment</li>\n                <li>Parrot OS/Kali → Penetration testing and ethical hacking</li>\n                <li>SecurityOnion → Network security monitoring and threat detection</li>\n                <li>Elastic Stack → Data ingestion, visualization, and analysis</li>\n            </ul>\n\n            <h2>Certifications & Progress</h2>\n            <ul>\n                <li>NET+ (N10-009)</li>\n                <li>SEC+ (SY0-701)</li>\n                <li>OCI Foundations Associate (1Z0-1085-25)</li>\n                <li>Microsoft Certified: Azure AI Fundamentals (AI-900)</li>\n                <li>CYSA+ (Loading...)</li>\n            </ul>\n        </article>\n    </main>\n</body>\n</html>"}}